name: DongHyuk Kim's Website
body:
## Welcome to **DongHyuk Kim's** website.
* This website is made for the CSE199 project.
* My major is Computer Science.
* We learn something through [`internet-class.org`](https://www.internet-class.org)

Our instructor is Geoffrey Challen  
He is **great instructor for computer science.**  
He is **passionate instructor.**

## In this course, we learn about  
* [The Internet Era](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvZZdQHM91vx-eHTJJOmQOEK)
* [Connectivity](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvYJqvvQkhHdMZ8_vgde_rVH)
* [Protocols](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvayBmPKnaIdgdYIKpuhpJoe)
* [Routing](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvZJs7DyfPgiUDovil2K7axM)
* [Transport](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvZdbYzA6om36xT-D-Tuew3F)
* [Naming](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvZgvqcZWzGHmqlcwr_1a3QK)
* [Web](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvaAtrsVGbdeNtwf-moYNq-E)
* [Search](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvYwbyXe-4FfJlcGbQPwMQKf)
* [Security](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvZL-Zi9r6wxbEvI2J1jF-JK)
* [Identity](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvaBrobQf5IsjobG27Wzdfkc)
* [The Interactive Web](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvYD3ZxVZin43SghUCH5DP6u)
* [The Mobile and Pervasive Web](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvacSuRzHvZDx7stAf-HtULR)
* [Your Brain on the Internet](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvbIDe0ol__bk5jNJLJlSDto)
* [Internet Content and Economics](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvYG2BzAodJLWZLI991llk83)
* [Lost and Future Visions of the Internet](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk97mPCd8nvZBmNg8Xcjbheq03IvYuFSC)  

## Is this class boring??? **NO!!!**  
**WHY?** because our class is well organized   

ACTIVITY | VIDEO | REVIEW
-------- | -------- | --------
We have fun activities every Monday and Wednesday | We have fun videos to watch every week | We have recitation every Friday to review and ask questions about topics  

* Every activity is extremely exciting and fun, so you would like to come to the class  
* Every video is fun and meaningful to watch, we learn lessons from videos  
* Every recitation is helpful, we are free to ask question what we want to know
